--> To Install on Android
1. To install android app on your device just install 'GitHub Clone.apk' file.

--> To Install on linux
2. To install linux app on your linux device
	1. open linux_app folder and then open terminal from this folder.
	2. now in terminal just run ./sample.
	3. thats it your app will run on linux.
	
--> To view source code
3. To view the source code open sample folder and open lib folder you will get access to all the source code of the app
